                        <div type="textpart" subtype="column" n="I">
                        <ab>
                          <lb n="1"/><unclear>ὁ</unclear> <unclear>δῆμος</unclear>
                          <lb n="2"/>ὁ <gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/><orig>υ</orig><gap reason="illegible" quantity="4" unit="character"/>
                          </ab>                            
                            <ab>
                                <lb n="3"/>ὁ <rs type="institution" subtype="assembly" role="dedicant" key="demos" ref="#gortyn"><w lemma="δῆμος">δῆ<supplied reason="lost">μος</supplied></w></rs>
                                <lb n="4"/>ὁ <placeName ref="#gortyn" type="ethnic">Γορτυνίων</placeName>
                            </ab>
                        </div>
                        <div type="textpart" subtype="column" n="II">
                        <ab>
                          <lb n="1"/><supplied reason="lost">ὁ δῆμος</supplied>
                          <lb n="2"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><orig>ω<unclear>τω</unclear>ι</orig><gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/>
                          </ab>                            
                            <ab>
                                <lb n="3"/>ὁ <rs type="institution" subtype="assembly" role="dedicant" key="demos" ref="#knossos"><w lemma="δῆμος">δῆμος</w></rs>
                                <lb n="4"/>ὁ <placeName ref="#knossos" type="ethnic">Κνωσίων</placeName>
                            </ab>
                        </div>
                        <div type="textpart" subtype="column" n="III">
                        <ab>
                          <lb n="1"/><supplied reason="lost">ὁ δῆμος</supplied>
                          <lb n="2"/>ὁ <placeName ref="#astypalaia" type="ethnic">Ἀσ<supplied reason="lost">τυπαλαιέων</supplied></placeName>
                          </ab>                            
                            <ab>
                                <lb n="3"/>ὁ <supplied reason="lost"><rs type="institution" subtype="assembly" role="dedicant" key="demos" ref="#phaistos"><w lemma="δῆμος">δῆμος</w></rs></supplied>
                                <lb n="4"/>ὁ <placeName ref="#phaistos" type="ethnic">Φαιστίων</placeName>
                            </ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div type="commentary">
                        <p>La lastra commemora più concessioni onorarie effettuate ad uno stesso individuo dal <foreign>demos</foreign> delle città menzionate, fra le quali figurano le cretesi Gortyna, Knossos e Phaistos.</p>
                <p><emph>Elementi istituzionali o altri termini rilevanti</emph>: <ref type="inst" target="#demos"><foreign>demos</foreign></ref>.</p>
